<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <title>전화번호 인증 비밀번호 찾기 · 일잘러</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
  <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: "Pretendard", -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #0a0f1e; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 24px; }
    .card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 24px; padding: 36px 28px; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; }
    .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: white; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .subtitle { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .desc { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    label { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    input { width: 100%; height: 52px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 14px; padding: 0 16px; font-size: 15px; font-family: inherit; color: white; outline: none; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    input:focus { border-color: #2563eb; }
    .btn { width: 100%; height: 52px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb, #3b82f6); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 14px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; margin-top: 10px; }
    .back { display: block; text-align: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 20px; }
    .alert { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3); color: #fca5a5; border-radius: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }
    .divider { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin:20px 0; }
    .divider span { font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); white-space:nowrap; }
    .divider hr { flex:1; border:none; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="logo">일잘러 🏗️</div>
    <div class="subtitle">인테리어 공정관리</div>

    <% if alert %>
      <div class="alert"><%= alert %></div>
    <% end %>

    <p class="desc">
      가입 시 등록한 이메일과 전화번호를 입력하시면<br>
      바로 비밀번호를 재설정할 수 있습니다.
    </p>

    <%= form_with url: phone_password_reset_action_path, method: :post, local: true do |f| %>
      <div>
        <label>이메일 주소</label>
        <%= f.email_field :email, placeholder: "email@example.com", required: true, value: params[:email] %>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label>가입 시 등록한 전화번호</label>
        <%= f.telephone_field :phone, placeholder: "010-1234-5678", required: true, value: params[:phone] %>
      </div>

      <div class="divider">
        <hr><span>새 비밀번호 설정</span><hr>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label>새 비밀번호 (8자 이상)</label>
        <%= f.password_field :password, placeholder: "새 비밀번호", required: true, minlength: 8 %>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label>비밀번호 확인</label>
        <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, placeholder: "비밀번호 확인", required: true %>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="btn">📱 전화번호 인증 후 비밀번호 변경</button>
    <% end %>

    <div class="divider">
      <hr><span>또는</span><hr>
    </div>

    <%= link_to "📧 이메일로 재설정하기", new_password_reset_path, class: "back", style: "margin-top:0;" %>
    <%= link_to "← 로그인으로 돌아가기", login_path, class: "back" %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
